                  </hi> I live at 398, Oxford Street—the curtains, china groups, and bronze figure were stolen from my premises—the curtains are worth 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. the pair—the guipure curtains are worth 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—the browse figure 8<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. or 9<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., and the china groups 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.</p>
               <p>
